name: T.Ray Mac
bio: Producer/Musician/Engineer from Miami         @jalisafaye’s New Single “STARTING OVER” is out NOW!! Produced by 🙋🏾‍♂️. Link below! 👇🏾👇🏾

social_posts.post_text:
🚨🚨🚨 IT’S TIME!!!!!!! It’s been a long journey but we’re finally here! @jalisafaye is dropping “Starting Over” The Album JANUARY 10TH!!! It’s even more special because that’s Her birthday! 🎉🎉

The album release concert is 10 days after on JANUARY 20TH‼️‼️ You’re gonna want to be in the building. The squad is locked and loaded! Admission is FREE. Make sure you save the date!! 

I’m so proud of the hard work Jalisa put into this record!! She’s a beast at everything she does so you know this will be special. The best to ever do it!!! I know this album will be a blessing to so many. I’m so grateful for the opportunity to do work with this genius and produce this album with so many other amazing talents. Y’all know my crew is all through this joint 💪🏾
I’m nervous of course 😂 but I’m ready. We’re ready! This is our baby lol. 💜#StartingOver2023 it’s happening!!! 
Be sure to SUBSCRIBE to Jalisa’s IG for all of the bts and exclusives. She’s letting y’all in on all of the magic! 
S/o my brother @kalibtracks /  @sevenfxcreative on the graphics!

Happy Monday!! Here’s a clip from last week In Houston w @official_flo and my bros @teajai1020, @wmgboowie ,@djkronik, and @eric_ez_e /Tammy lol who felt like getting extra saucy on the bridge, so you know i had to join in! 😂🤘🏾🤘🏾#StartingOver2023
Happy Thursday! I posted this on my story last week but here it is for the timeline! Some Drum and Synth Bass 🔒 with my brotha @teajai1020 on “Low”.

It’s Christmas Eve! Here’s the end of a version of “Christmas Time Is Here”  @jalisafaye and i did a few years back. You can check out the full version on my page somewhere lol. Jalisa absolutely blazed this joint and I was just happy to play a lil part 😂🙌🏾. One of my favorite projects that we’ve worked on as a production/writing/creative duo. I can’t wait for you guys to hear more of what we’ve been cooking on “StartingOverTheAlbum”! 
Jan 10th!!!! We’ve got even more surprises in January 👀‼️
Stay tuned!!!

The Album is dropping in 2 days!! I’m super excited for y’all to hear the work @jalisafaye and i put in!! 

Here’s a quick preview of one of the records on the album featuring my brother @v_keys023 , Who co produced/mixed a lotttt of this record with me!! 💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾. This melody had been ringing in my head for a minute. God gave me the words to the chorus then J and V took it and ran with it! A big part of “Starting Over” is to simply “Let Go”!

Why you keep looking back? Let Go Of That!! There’s plenty of things to look at, but don’t look back! You can’t hold on to the past, LET GO OF THAT!! 

The release concert is in 12 days!! Make sure you get your tickets!! And bring someone! A friend, a family member, your boo 😂 ANYBODY!! It’s gonna be a night to remember. #StartingOver2023
Admission is FREE and VIP is $30! Link in @jalisafaye ‘s bio!

Today is a HOLIDAY!!! 🎉🥳🎂
Happy Birthday to the Beautiful, Intelligent, Talented, Gifted, Funny, Outgoing, Caring, Understanding, Anointed, and All Around Loving Person that is @jalisafaye ! I can’t even try to describe all the things you are to so many! Not only is it your birthday but you birthed an album today too!! I’m soooo proud of what “Starting Over The Album” came to be! Jalisa has literally put her blood sweat and tears into this record yall!! I’m just grateful to be apart of the journey with you J. We couldn’t see it at 17yrs old when we met but God had a plan for us even then! I love you!!! 💜💜 I’m forever thankful for you. I pray this year is everything you need and more. 1/10/23 will be a milestone for you! It’s lit all month y’all!!! If you want to send her a gift or sow into her album/release concert, her cashapp is: $Jalisafaye or Zelle: Teamjfaye@gmail.com. 

STARTING OVER THE ALBUM IS OUT NOW!!!! Let us know your favorite song so far!!!

Top 10?! God is Great 😩! 
@jalisafaye dropped her album “Starting Over” yesterday and we’ve been  in the top 10 since then! THANK YOU FOR YOUR SUPPORT!! Everyone who’s called, texted, purchased the record, streamed, reposted, told a friend, allat, We really appreciate it!!! I pray there’s a message or messages on this album for everybody and that you’re refreshed during/after every listen. Jalisa poured her heart into this!! Tell a friend! It’s a great time to START OVER! #StartingOver2023

Here’s some Behind The Scenes footage doing some vocal arranging on “Jesus I Believe” from @jalisafaye’s album “Starting Over” with @v_keys023! @aleshia.gotkeys was in the live room recording soprano but me and Vaughn were already plotting on the tenor notes lol. Jalisa is sitting there between us with her head down TIED lol. She worked hard that day. 
Swipe for the results ➡️➡️➡️ I’m proud of what this record came out to be! ALBUM OUT EVERYWHERE NOW!!! GO GET IT! #StartingOver2023

🚨🗣️SHOW WEEEEEK! Starting Over Album Release CONCERT is HAPPENING THIS FRIDAY AT 7:30pm @redeemingword 🥳🥳🥳• LINK IN BIO FOR TICKETS • GENERAL ADMISSION FREE, VIP $30 • I’m eager to sing this songs WITH YALL cause I see y’all learning these lyrics everyday! 😂🥹 Go get the album if you haven’t already! Available everywhere DIGITALLY!

HAPPY WEDNESDAY! 
Here’s some behind the scenes footage of my cousin @dchiv cutting drums on “You Made It Right” from @jalisafaye’s album “Starting Over”. We were trying to figure out the intro. Most of the time when I start a record from scratch or do a key drum reference, I have Dave in mind lol! For some reason he chooses to still play some of my ideas 😂. I’m so happy to have the master/and my blood 🩸 on most of the records on this album. And you knowwww he’s gonna be in the building FRIDAY! So Pull up!!! You don’t want to miss this release concert. SWIPE for the first reference of this song, and the final result! ➡️➡️➡️➡️ 
S/o my bros @eric_ez_e , @dminus__jr who blazed on this joint! And my brother @jamahlsmith11 who stepped in early on in this record and put his sauce on it!! 💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾
Tomorrow is the day ‼️‼️ We’re excited and ready!! Admission is FREE. If you’re in South Florida I want to see your face in the place!! @jalisafaye

Today’s the day!! 

It’s been a journey but we’re finally here! All roads lead to Redeeming Word Christian Center tonight for @jalisafaye’s Album Release Concert! We’re excited! 
I got my brothers rockin with me tonight @v_keys023 @dchiv @dminus__jr @saintorbin81 so you know it’s gonna be special! The bgvs are locked and ready too! Admission is free but you can get tickets at the link in Jalisa’s bio. Doors open at 7 and we start at 7:30!! Pull up!! Tell a friend!! Tell everybody! Bring somebody with you!! 🎬: @teajai1020 💪🏾💪🏾 #StartingOver #StartingOver2023

Happy Monday! 
Today makes one month since the album release concert! Andddd a little over a month since the actual release of @jalisafaye’s Album “Starting Over”. I’m so grateful for all of the support and love shown so far! If you haven’t grabbed the album GO GET IT NOW! I can’t wait for you guys to hear “Starting Over Live”! 😎 Here’s a clip of “Jesus I Believe” from the concert. It got pretty crazy in there🕺🏾. Let us know your favorite song on the record!
Last Week In Arlington, Texas With The Boss Man @official_flo #GreenLight
Drum & Bass View From Last Week In Texas w @official_flo

Happy 2️⃣9️⃣th Birthday To Me!!! Grateful to see another year! 28 was filled with some crazy ups and downs but I’m just happy to still be here! I’ve been MIA for a min but things are about to change 😎Thank y’all for all the love so far!

Living 

📸: @teajai1020

Blessed To Do What I Love! 🤘🏾
Happy Sunday! 🙏🏾

Happy 29th Birthday to the best to ever do it! The one that’s had my back no matter what! You already know how proud I am of who you’ve become! From 17-29 ( We been rocking for 12 years 😩. Time Flies lol ) 
I’m looking forward to everything 29 has for you!! I love you Falisa Jaye 😂💜💜 @jalisafaye
